msg: Fix "Dead assignment" issue identified by clang-analyzer, in Socket.sendto().
I expect that this bug would have lead to a memory leak, as GetByteArrayElements was not followed by ReleaseByteArrayElements.
This method is never called by the current Tomcat 8, 7 or 6.
Not tested, but an obvious fix.
